title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 24 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 24 2022
description:
Clay and Buck analyze the Ukraine crisis with guest Steve Yates, Senior Fellow at the America First Policy Institute and former deputy national security advisor to VP Cheney. What did Biden mean by his no comment on China? Biden contradicts Harris on the purpose of sanctions. Dr. Leana Wen discovers remote learning, masks hurt development of children. C&B take calls to close the show.
